     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-1-1- Place the device providing 2bar of pressure in the reservoir With No Brake Pedal Pressed",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 975,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 7080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "-1-2- Open the bleeder screw 1 of the Pedal Feel Simulator (Reservoir to PFS)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1200,
